{"tid":1506810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"：不如我地再勇武啲？","createTime":"2019-08-26T02:18:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T20:48:06.000Z","uid":16713,"like":84,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9a21d735596f816f375dfb4a33094a031a81e6c3","tid":1506810,"uid":16713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:18:19.000Z","msg":"我今日咁樣問自己<br />\n其實前線既人真係唔多<br />\n如果可以再多啲 可以做到既野就更多 更快 更強 更有效<br />\n<br />\n之後我問我班朋友 不如下次再勇武啲 唔好怕<br />\n佢地都話好 我地有既係團結既力量<br />\n<br />\n兄弟，前線見"},{"pid":"dbf3eb4fc47e4fbec7a6c3630ac4fae803ec2cd4","tid":1506810,"uid":51701,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:24:58.000Z","msg":"講真路油汽都唔割<br />\n仲驚乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一粒救十人"},{"pid":"d2dd143d8261bfcf1e0f2c9f07505c31d8e790f9","tid":1506810,"uid":215487,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:28:30.000Z","msg":"前線已經一路勇緊。係差人數。但新兵真心要諗清楚。"},{"pid":"2722cbdaaaf1bb7dcb49eff10215617a8b3722cc","tid":1506810,"uid":16713,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"d2dd143d8261bfcf1e0f2c9f07505c31d8e790f9","tid":1506810,"uid":215487,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:28:30.000Z","msg":"前線已經一路勇緊。係差人數。但新兵真心要諗清楚。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:36:15.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n希望多啲人有覺悟<br />\n如果依家所有既中後排都可以成為前線，<br />\n咁就唔洗再分勇與唔勇<br />\n全隊，由頭到尾，都會係至撚勇嗰班<br />\n我地可以做到既事就多好多了"},{"pid":"81609ce14eeaf98d10353b2eaf917d43939ed13f","tid":1506810,"uid":215487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2722cbdaaaf1bb7dcb49eff10215617a8b3722cc","tid":1506810,"uid":16713,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"d2dd143d8261bfcf1e0f2c9f07505c31d8e790f9","tid":1506810,"uid":215487,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:28:30.000Z","msg":"前線已經一路勇緊。係差人數。但新兵真心要諗清楚。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:36:15.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n希望多啲人有覺悟<br />\n如果依家所有既中後排都可以成為前線，<br />\n咁就唔洗再分